							</div>
						</div>
					
					<div class="row">
						
						<p>Much of the NSA’s defence is that the public should be unconcerned, summed up by the dictum: “If you have nothing to hide, you have nothing to fear.” But civil liberties groups such as the Electronic Frontier Foundation and the American Civil Liberties Union warn that surveillance goes well beyond what Congress intended and what the US constitution allows.</p>
					</div>
					
						<div class="row no-ie">
			<div class="span8 offset2">
				<div class="video-player-wrapper" id="video-102-container">
					<div id="video102"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="span8 offset2 video-player-info">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="span2">
