							<div class="f-mod-lbl f-serif-i">Chris Soghoian</div>
							<div class="f-sans f-mod-sub f-red">Principal technologist, ACLU <div class="share-i" gia-link="video/102">
<div class="i-share share-link"></div>
<div class="i-share share-twt" gia-link-type="twitter" gia-link-text="&quot;If the NSA wants to get into your computer or phone, they're gonna get in.&quot; @csoghoian on #NSAFiles Decoded"></div>
