						<div class="row">

							<p>Not all companies have complied. Ladar Levison, the founder of Lavabit — a small, secure email provider used by Snowden — suspended operations in August rather than comply with a warrant that would have allowed the US government access to the data of all Lavabit’s 400,000 customers.</p>
						</div>	

							<div class="row no-ie">
			<div class="span8 offset2">
				<div class="video-player-wrapper" id="video-112-container">
